      "infoHTML": "<h3>Tono Neutro ⚪</h3>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px;\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">N°</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;\">0</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Marca</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-size:24px;\">a</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Descripción</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;\">Corto y suave, sin acento ni énfasis</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Ejemplo</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-size:20px;\">ma</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Pronunciación</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;\">ma (rápido, débil)</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Español</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;\">Partícula interrogativa</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;font-weight:bold;\">Frase</td><td style=\"padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #555;\">Nǐ hǎo ma? (你好吗?) = ¿Cómo estás?</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-top:10px;color:#aaa;\">🔊 No tiene marca diacrítica. Se pronuncia ligero y sin énfasis.</p>"
    },
